description.narrative: This project aims to deliver inclusive climate mitigation to investors, and co-packages resilience/ecosystem services and carbon sequestration into an accessible interface for investors to buy impact and monitor progress. At the same time it enables the inclusion of smallholder farmers into ecosystem services markets and incentivises the adoption of regenerative and climate smart farming practices. FarmImpact serves as a gatekeeper for farmers data and ensure farmers are compensated for their impact in a fair manner (FairData).
